    "content": {
      "scenario": "Minimal Pair 🎯: /ɪ/ vs /iː/ (EN)",
      "text": "<div style='margin-bottom:10px'><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank' style='background:#1565C0;color:white;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:5px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88em;font-family:sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin:2px;'>🔊 /ɪ/</a>&nbsp;<a href='https://forvo.com/word/sheep/#en' target='_blank' style='background:#4CAF50;color:white;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:5px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88em;font-family:sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin:2px;'>🔊 /iː/</a>&nbsp;<a href='http://www.ipachart.com/' target='_blank' style='background:#6A1B9A;color:white;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:5px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88em;font-family:sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin:2px;'>📖 IPAchart</a></div><b>Phoneme A</b> <code>/ɪ/</code><br><b>IPA description:</b> {{c1::short, relaxed, mid-high front vowel}}",
      "explanation": "<b>/ɪ/</b> — short, relaxed, mid-high front vowel<br><b>/iː/</b> — long, tense, high front vowel<br><br><b>🧠 Articulatory Tip (ES):</b> Para /ɪ/, relaja la boca y la lengua completamente. Es corta. Para /iː/, sonríe exageradamente y tensa los lados de la lengua. Es más larga.<br><br><table border='1' cellpadding='5' style='border-collapse:collapse;width:100%'><thead style='background:#E3F2FD'><tr><th>Word A (/ɪ/)</th><th>IPA A</th><th>Word B (/iː/)</th><th>IPA B</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>ship</b></td><td><code>/ʃɪp/</code></td><td><b>sheep</b></td><td><code>/ʃiːp/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>bit</b></td><td><code>/bɪt/</code></td><td><b>beat</b></td><td><code>/biːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>sit</b></td><td><code>/sɪt/</code></td><td><b>seat</b></td><td><code>/siːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>fit</b></td><td><code>/fɪt/</code></td><td><b>feet</b></td><td><code>/fiːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>fill</b></td><td><code>/fɪl/</code></td><td><b>feel</b></td><td><code>/fiːl/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>grin</b></td><td><code>/ɡrɪn/</code></td><td><b>green</b></td><td><code>/ɡriːn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>slip</b></td><td><code>/slɪp/</code></td><td><b>sleep</b></td><td><code>/sliːp/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>hit</b></td><td><code>/hɪt/</code></td><td><b>heat</b></td><td><code>/hiːt/</code></td></tr></tbody></table>",
      "spanish": "Para /ɪ/, relaja la boca y la lengua completamente. Es corta. Para /iː/, sonríe exageradamente y tensa los lados de la lengua. Es más larga.",
      "usage": "<table border='1' cellpadding='5' style='border-collapse:collapse;width:100%'><thead style='background:#E3F2FD'><tr><th>Word A (/ɪ/)</th><th>IPA A</th><th>Word B (/iː/)</th><th>IPA B</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>ship</b></td><td><code>/ʃɪp/</code></td><td><b>sheep</b></td><td><code>/ʃiːp/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>bit</b></td><td><code>/bɪt/</code></td><td><b>beat</b></td><td><code>/biːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>sit</b></td><td><code>/sɪt/</code></td><td><b>seat</b></td><td><code>/siːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>fit</b></td><td><code>/fɪt/</code></td><td><b>feet</b></td><td><code>/fiːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>fill</b></td><td><code>/fɪl/</code></td><td><b>feel</b></td><td><code>/fiːl/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>grin</b></td><td><code>/ɡrɪn/</code></td><td><b>green</b></td><td><code>/ɡriːn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>slip</b></td><td><code>/slɪp/</code></td><td><b>sleep</b></td><td><code>/sliːp/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>hit</b></td><td><code>/hɪt/</code></td><td><b>heat</b></td><td><code>/hiːt/</code></td></tr></tbody></table>",
