      "scenario": "Minimal Pair 🎯: /ʌ/ vs /ɑː/ (EN)",
      "text": "<div style='margin-bottom:10px'><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank' style='background:#1565C0;color:white;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:5px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88em;font-family:sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin:2px;'>🔊 /ʌ/</a>&nbsp;<a href='https://forvo.com/word/cop/#en' target='_blank' style='background:#4CAF50;color:white;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:5px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88em;font-family:sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin:2px;'>🔊 /ɑː/</a>&nbsp;<a href='http://www.ipachart.com/' target='_blank' style='background:#6A1B9A;color:white;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:5px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88em;font-family:sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin:2px;'>📖 IPAchart</a></div><b>Phoneme A</b> <code>/ʌ/</code><br><b>IPA description:</b> {{c1::short, open-mid back unrounded vowel}}",
      "explanation": "<b>/ʌ/</b> — short, open-mid back unrounded vowel<br><b>/ɑː/</b> — long, open back unrounded vowel<br><br><b>🧠 Articulatory Tip (ES):</b> Para /ʌ/, haz un sonido neutro y corto como si te hubieran golpeado levemente en el estómago. Para /ɑː/, abre la boca completamente hacia abajo como cuando el doctor te examina la garganta.<br><br><table border='1' cellpadding='5' style='border-collapse:collapse;width:100%'><thead style='background:#E3F2FD'><tr><th>Word A (/ʌ/)</th><th>IPA A</th><th>Word B (/ɑː/)</th><th>IPA B</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>cup</b></td><td><code>/kʌp/</code></td><td><b>cop</b></td><td><code>/kɑːp/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>cut</b></td><td><code>/kʌt/</code></td><td><b>cot</b></td><td><code>/kɑːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>hut</b></td><td><code>/hʌt/</code></td><td><b>hot</b></td><td><code>/hɑːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>duck</b></td><td><code>/dʌk/</code></td><td><b>dock</b></td><td><code>/dɑːk/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>run</b></td><td><code>/rʌn/</code></td><td><b>Ron</b></td><td><code>/rɑːn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>nut</b></td><td><code>/nʌt/</code></td><td><b>not</b></td><td><code>/nɑːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>but</b></td><td><code>/bʌt/</code></td><td><b>bought</b></td><td><code>/bɔːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>suck</b></td><td><code>/sʌk/</code></td><td><b>sock</b></td><td><code>/sɑːk/</code></td></tr></tbody></table>",
      "spanish": "Para /ʌ/, haz un sonido neutro y corto como si te hubieran golpeado levemente en el estómago. Para /ɑː/, abre la boca completamente hacia abajo como cuando el doctor te examina la garganta.",
      "usage": "<table border='1' cellpadding='5' style='border-collapse:collapse;width:100%'><thead style='background:#E3F2FD'><tr><th>Word A (/ʌ/)</th><th>IPA A</th><th>Word B (/ɑː/)</th><th>IPA B</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>cup</b></td><td><code>/kʌp/</code></td><td><b>cop</b></td><td><code>/kɑːp/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>cut</b></td><td><code>/kʌt/</code></td><td><b>cot</b></td><td><code>/kɑːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>hut</b></td><td><code>/hʌt/</code></td><td><b>hot</b></td><td><code>/hɑːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>duck</b></td><td><code>/dʌk/</code></td><td><b>dock</b></td><td><code>/dɑːk/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>run</b></td><td><code>/rʌn/</code></td><td><b>Ron</b></td><td><code>/rɑːn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>nut</b></td><td><code>/nʌt/</code></td><td><b>not</b></td><td><code>/nɑːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>but</b></td><td><code>/bʌt/</code></td><td><b>bought</b></td><td><code>/bɔːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/cup/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>suck</b></td><td><code>/sʌk/</code></td><td><b>sock</b></td><td><code>/sɑːk/</code></td></tr></tbody></table>",
