    "content": {
      "scenario": "Minimal Pair 🎯: /æ/ vs /ɛ/ (EN)",
      "text": "<div style='margin-bottom:10px'><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank' style='background:#1565C0;color:white;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:5px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88em;font-family:sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin:2px;'>🔊 /æ/</a>&nbsp;<a href='https://forvo.com/word/bed/#en' target='_blank' style='background:#4CAF50;color:white;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:5px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88em;font-family:sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin:2px;'>🔊 /ɛ/</a>&nbsp;<a href='http://www.ipachart.com/' target='_blank' style='background:#6A1B9A;color:white;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:5px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88em;font-family:sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin:2px;'>📖 IPAchart</a></div><b>Phoneme A</b> <code>/æ/</code><br><b>IPA description:</b> {{c1::short, near-open front unrounded vowel}}",
      "explanation": "<b>/æ/</b> — short, near-open front unrounded vowel<br><b>/ɛ/</b> — short, open-mid front unrounded vowel<br><br><b>🧠 Articulatory Tip (ES):</b> Para /æ/, abre la boca de manera lateral (sonrisa exagerada) y empuja la lengua hacia adelante y abajo. Para /ɛ/, abre la boca de manera neutra (parecido a la 'e' de cama).<br><br><table border='1' cellpadding='5' style='border-collapse:collapse;width:100%'><thead style='background:#E3F2FD'><tr><th>Word A (/æ/)</th><th>IPA A</th><th>Word B (/ɛ/)</th><th>IPA B</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>bad</b></td><td><code>/bæd/</code></td><td><b>bed</b></td><td><code>/bɛd/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>man</b></td><td><code>/mæn/</code></td><td><b>men</b></td><td><code>/mɛn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>sad</b></td><td><code>/sæd/</code></td><td><b>said</b></td><td><code>/sɛd/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>pan</b></td><td><code>/pæn/</code></td><td><b>pen</b></td><td><code>/pɛn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>tan</b></td><td><code>/tæn/</code></td><td><b>ten</b></td><td><code>/tɛn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>bag</b></td><td><code>/bæg/</code></td><td><b>beg</b></td><td><code>/bɛg/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>dad</b></td><td><code>/dæd/</code></td><td><b>dead</b></td><td><code>/dɛd/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>land</b></td><td><code>/lænd/</code></td><td><b>lend</b></td><td><code>/lɛnd/</code></td></tr></tbody></table>",
      "spanish": "Para /æ/, abre la boca de manera lateral (sonrisa exagerada) y empuja la lengua hacia adelante y abajo. Para /ɛ/, abre la boca de manera neutra (parecido a la 'e' de cama).",
      "usage": "<table border='1' cellpadding='5' style='border-collapse:collapse;width:100%'><thead style='background:#E3F2FD'><tr><th>Word A (/æ/)</th><th>IPA A</th><th>Word B (/ɛ/)</th><th>IPA B</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>bad</b></td><td><code>/bæd/</code></td><td><b>bed</b></td><td><code>/bɛd/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>man</b></td><td><code>/mæn/</code></td><td><b>men</b></td><td><code>/mɛn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>sad</b></td><td><code>/sæd/</code></td><td><b>said</b></td><td><code>/sɛd/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>pan</b></td><td><code>/pæn/</code></td><td><b>pen</b></td><td><code>/pɛn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>tan</b></td><td><code>/tæn/</code></td><td><b>ten</b></td><td><code>/tɛn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>bag</b></td><td><code>/bæg/</code></td><td><b>beg</b></td><td><code>/bɛg/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>dad</b></td><td><code>/dæd/</code></td><td><b>dead</b></td><td><code>/dɛd/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>land</b></td><td><code>/lænd/</code></td><td><b>lend</b></td><td><code>/lɛnd/</code></td></tr></tbody></table>",
